### Criar uma order (REST – Chi)
POST http://localhost:8080/order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer": "Maria Silva",
  "description": "Pedido de teste",
  "amount": 99.9
}

### Listar orders (REST) — GET /order
GET http://localhost:8080/order

### GraphQL (gqlgen) — listOrders e createOrder — API em /query (ver playground em /)
POST http://localhost:8081/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query { listOrders { id customer description amount createdAt } }"
}

### gRPC — ListOrders (reflection ativada)
# grpcurl -plaintext -d '{}' localhost:50051 order.v1.OrderService/ListOrders
